### Phase 4 — match-scoped live location (REST §3.2)
#
# Prerequisites: same auth flow as phase3.http — set @token from verify-otp.
#
# 1. GET /me — profile includes locationSharingEnabled (default false).
# 2. POST /me/location without sharing → 403 LOCATION_SHARING_OFF.
# 3. PUT /me/location-sharing { "enabled": true } → 200.
# 4. POST /me/location → 200.
# 5. Rapid second POST → 429 RATE_LIMITED (default min interval 1000 ms).

@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@token   = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### GET me (see profile.locationSharingEnabled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST location — expects403 if sharing off
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 5.6037,
  "longitude": -0.187
}

### Enable location sharing
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/location-sharing
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": true
}

### POST location — expects 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 5.6037,
  "longitude": -0.187,
  "recordedAt": "2026-04-10T12:00:00Z"
}

### Disable sharing
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/location-sharing
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": false
}
